{"tid":1827922,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[1.19 中環見] 不是有希望才堅持 是堅持了才有希望","createTime":"2020-01-17T10:51:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T06:10:42.000Z","uid":42194,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"190dace43d071069930872807b673b8db125a415","tid":1827922,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T10:51:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bhMrpZJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbhMrpZJ.jpg&h=cd173b16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">不是有希望才堅持<br />\n是堅持了才有希望</span></span><br />\n<br />\n屢次被反對、被打壓<br />\n眼見自由逐步收窄<br />\n面對極權，香港人從未言退<br />\n<br />\n光復香港、齊上齊落從來都不止是口號；民間集會團隊手足正用我哋嘅方式去堅持、去延續呢場運動同希望。<br />\n<br />\n請大家繼續同我哋喺中環見，向國際展示我哋係唔會輕易向極權屈服。<br />\n<br />\n就算反對左香港地區嘅遊行，全球仲有31個城市嘅手足與我哋同行。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，堅持！<br />\n和理優，反抗！<br />\n<br />\n應承我哋，不習慣、不屈服、不妥協、不麻木，於黎明嚟到嘅一日，煲底見。<br />\n<br />\n你若放棄 誰衛我城<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n願榮光歸香港<br />\n<br />\n1.19 中環見！<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n2020 港共受刑<br />\n立即民主政改 否則天下制裁<br />\n2020 Karma to Commies<br />\nUniversal Siege on Communists<br />\n=========================<br />\n1.19天下制裁集會<br />\n立即民主政改 否則天下制裁<br />\n<br />\n日期：2020年1月19日(日)<br />\n時間：15：00<br />\n地點：遮打道及遮打花園<br />\n主辦：民間集會團隊<br />\n*集會獲發不反對通知書，而遊行獲發反對通知書<br />\n<br />\n1.19 Universal Siege on Communists Assembly<br />\n<br />\nDate: 19/1/2020 (Sun)<br />\nTime: 3PM<br />\nVenue: Chater Road and Chater Garden<br />\nOrganiser: HKCATeam<br />\n*Letter of No Objection for assembly Obtained, Letter of Objection for March Obtained<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n支持民間集會團隊（眾籌/參與）：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/s/HKCATeam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fs%2FHKCATeam&d=yrakYkBpMe8E3VCHF0kcyvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=5a437272\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/s/HKCATeam</a><br />\n參與/洽詢合作：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/HKCATeam_bot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKCATeam_bot&d=yrakYkBpMe8E3VCHF0kcyvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=02c8ec53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKCATeam_bot</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n我們的最新動向/合作洽詢：<br />\nFacebook：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKCATeam/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKCATeam%2F&d=yrakYkBpMe8E3VCHF0kcyvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=0447843e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKCATeam/</a><br />\nInstagram：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/HKCAT/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2FHKCAT%2F&d=yrakYkBpMe8E3VCHF0kcyvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=d60ea331\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/HKCAT/</a><br />\nTwitter：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/HKCATeam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKCATeam&d=yrakYkBpMe8E3VCHF0kcyvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=6769e36a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/HKCATeam</a>"},{"pid":"033ebe2a368f89891c09a506166346db726b7e85","tid":1827922,"uid":233156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T10:52:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ad6d78231cebac9dd390361212fa4743a0f8573e","tid":1827922,"uid":42194,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T10:53:05.000Z","msg":"1.19 中環見<br />\n不是有希望才堅持<br />\n是堅持了才有希望<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"641d784616c371b1a840da216f0983e45440660c","tid":1827922,"uid":307927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":